{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "将工坊搬至圣城的三姐妹\\n仍有一桩心事未了——\\n她们尚未与罗卡族铁匠拉兹莉决出高下。\\n三姐妹决定参加铁匠大赛“最佳铁匠杯”，\\n并开始打造参赛用的剑。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "三姐妹将工坊搬到圣城后\\n不久……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "你要的100支箭已经做好了。\\n应该没有问题，但姑且还是检查一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "噢噢，已经做好了！？\\n真是一如既往地快啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "是啊，罗吉娜三姐妹能来到这座城，\\n真是太好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "在这里的生活还习惯吗？\\n如果有什么困扰就告诉我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "完全没有！\\n罗吉姐和雷吉姐也这么认为吧！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "是啊，尤蒂尔\\n不仅像刚才那样关心我们……\\n还交给我们许多有意义的工作……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "真的……没有任何不满呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "嗯？罗吉娜？\\n说谎可不好哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "咦！？姐、姐姐？\\n我没有说谎啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "下一届最佳铁匠杯……\\n听说拉兹莉也会参加哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "她会参加！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？拉兹莉是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "罗卡族的铁匠，\\n是我们的老对手了……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "罗卡族！？\\n那群人都很擅长锻造，\\n跟他们竞争想必很不容易吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "没错！好多客人都被\\n拉兹莉的工坊抢走……\\n真是太不甘心了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "我们从父亲手上继承的技术，\\n不会输给任何人！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "不过……正如姐姐所说，\\n我刚才说谎了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "虽然并不后悔把工坊搬来这里……\\n可也因此没能跟拉兹莉做个了断，\\n总觉得有些遗憾。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "但如果在最佳铁匠杯上……\\n我一定能在比拼锻造技术的大赛上\\n跟拉兹莉一决胜负！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "谢谢你，姐姐……\\n谢谢你告诉我关于拉兹莉的事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "呵呵，不客气～\\n这都是为了我可爱的妹妹。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "在大赛中一举夺冠……听起来真棒！\\n既然决定要参赛，\\n就得抓紧打造参赛的武器了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "我觉得斧子比较好，\\n看起来又大又醒目……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "这种大型武器，没有强大的火力\\n和精湛的锻打技术就无法打造出\\n上乘的斧子，是对基本功的考验。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "我觉得刀比较好呢～\\n打造出锋利而漂亮的利刃，\\n不也是锻造的基础吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "听我说听我说～\\n要说锻造的基础，果然还是短剑吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "短剑都做不出的铁匠\\n哪做得出别的武器！\\n俗话不是说“嘲短剑者，必尝其利”吗！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "有、有这种说法吗……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "唔……总之你们都想在\\n锻造的基本功上一决高下吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "对！以华丽的装饰或奇特的造型\\n来哗众取宠什么的，根本就是歪门邪道！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "没错，卢吉娜说得对。\\n忠于基础，将品质做到最好……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "这就是我们从父亲那里\\n继承下来的锻造理念。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "继承自父亲的锻造理念吗……\\n那利吉最擅长的武器是？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "最擅长……虽然父亲什么武器都能做，\\n但最擅长的应该还是剑吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "是啊～父亲的剑\\n坚韧而美丽，是最棒的剑♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那么，用剑参赛如何？\\n打造一把不逊于利吉的剑。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "这样一来也能证明\\n你们继承了父亲的本领。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "三姐妹",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "诶、咦？难道我说了\\n什么不该说的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "啊……不是！那个……\\n正如你所言……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "做出不逊于父亲的剑吗……\\n是啊，这或许是个不错的目标。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "呵呵呵……我热血沸腾起来了！\\n要成为最棒的铁匠，\\n就得超越父亲才行！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "等等，卢吉娜！超越父亲什么的，\\n你说得倒轻巧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "不是挺好的吗～\\n想做出最棒的剑，\\n这种程度的决心是必需的♪",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110265_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢吉娜",
            "context": "对吧！？那你们听我说，\\n我刚才灵光一现！剑的形状要这样……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110263_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "罗吉娜",
            "context": "不行，那样的话强度会出问题。\\n剑的话，要更加……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110264_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "雷吉娜",
            "context": "呵呵♪看来能做出一把好剑呢，\\n真令人期待～",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20808_02_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}